<paragraph blockId="18.[264,1325,1140,1326]" pageId="18" pageNumber="19">Diagnosis. Six dc, 6 irregularly paired acr, hairs and bristles on thorax brown. Hind tarsomere 1 with 15–16 black ventral bristles on basal 1/5. Epandrium with long and wide lateral process; surstylus rather wide; cercus broad with acute apex; hypandrium with apical incision.</paragraph>
